- Verify the "Prevent concurrent login" option is checked.

If the "Prevent concurrent login" option is not checked, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA></STIG_DATA><STIG_DATA><VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE><ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure IBM Aspera Console to prevent concurrent logins for all accounts: 

