- Select the "Server" tab.
- Select the "Configuration" tab.
- Select the "Security" section.
- Verify the "Faspex accounts" "Use strong passwords" option is checked.

If the "Use strong passwords" option is not checked, this is a finding.

If the "Use strong passwords" option is checked, downgrade this requirement to a CAT III.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA></STIG_DATA><STIG_DATA><VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE><ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure IBM Aspera Faspex to require password complexity: 

