- Verify the "Faspex accounts" "Prevent passwords reuse" options is set to "5" or more.

If the "Prevent passwords reuse" options is less than "5" or the option is not checked, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA></STIG_DATA><STIG_DATA><VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE><ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure IBM Aspera Faspex passwords to be prohibited from reuse for a minimum of five generations: 

