- Scroll down to the "Security" section.
- Select the "User Security" option.
- Verify the "Session timeout" option is set to "10" minutes or less.

If the "Session timeout" option is set to more than "10" minutes, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA></STIG_DATA><STIG_DATA><VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE><ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure IBM Aspera Shares interactive session to terminated after 10 minutes of inactivity for non-privileged and privileged sessions: 

