- Log in to the IBM Aspera Shares web page as a user with administrative privilege. 
- Select the "Admin" tab.
- Scroll down to the "System Settings" section.
- Select the "Transfers" option.
- Verify the "Encryption at rest" option is set to "Required".

If the "Encryption at rest" option is set to "Optional" or is not set, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA></STIG_DATA><STIG_DATA><VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE><ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the IBM Aspera Shares to implement cryptographic mechanisms to prevent unauthorized disclosure or modification of all information that requires at rest protection.

